<task id="task_wsl_1rd_lp">
    <title>Editing entities from the editor</title>
    <shortdesc>You can add qualifying information to the RDF entities added to the document. You can
        edit the entities within the editor by right-clicking. This information can be edited at any
        time.</shortdesc>
