    <taskbody>
        <steps>
            <step>
                <cmd>Highlight the text that makes up the entity.<image placement="break"
                        href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A40f1e7f1-7347-4e62-af31-7c82a9f939ed/datastream/OBJ/view"
                        id="image_nc2_5rd_lp" align="center" height="3in" width="5in"/></cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Right-click on the highlighted text and choose the "Edit tag" option.<image
                        placement="break"
                        href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A77e19de4-de9a-487c-a8c5-78e9305fa475/datastream/OBJ/view"
                        id="image_hkp_1sd_lp" align="center" height="3in" width="5in"/></cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Edit any information in the pop-up you would like and click "Save."</cmd>
                <info>None of the information in the pop-up is required.<image placement="break"
                        href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A807338fa-4dd2-4be6-bb84-09ea58560e57/datastream/OBJ/view"
                        id="image_myh_dsd_lp" align="center" height="3in" width="5in"/></info>
            </step>
        </steps>
        <result>The edited information will appear in the left "Entities" column. Click on the entry
            to see the information attached to that particular entity. <image placement="break"
                href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A1155d498-13a9-47b0-b949-3acf2960db61/datastream/OBJ/view"
                id="image_w3z_fsd_lp" align="center" height="3in" width="5in"/></result>
    </taskbody>
</task>
